snippet.title: Fast & Furious Spy Racers: Rise of SH1FT3R | Announce Trailer | USA
snippet.description:
The criminal racing organization, SH1FT3R, is back! Use innovative gadgets and tear up the tracks in a globe-trotting tournament. Play as Tony Toretto and the Spy Racers in a bid to stop SH1FT3R from winning the ultimate high-tech vehicle! 

#FastAndFuriousSpyRacers #RiseOfSH1FT3R is coming in November to Nintendo Switch PlayStation Xbox & PC! 🏁🏎🏁 

Learn more 👉 https://outrightgames.com/us/games/fast-furious-spy-racers-rise-of-sh1ft3r
